@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@inject UserManager<ApplicationUser> UserManager
@inject RoleManager<IdentityRole> RoleManager
@model IEnumerable<Online_Language_School.Models.ApplicationUser>

<h4>Users Management</h4>
<table class="table table-striped">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Full Name</th>
            <th>Email</th>
            <th>Role</th>
            <th>Active</th>
            <th>Actions</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        @foreach (var user in Model)
        {
                <tr>
                    <td>@user.FirstName @user.LastName</td>
                    <td>@user.Email</td>
                    <td>
                        @{
                            var roles = await UserManager.GetRolesAsync(user);
                        }
                        @string.Join(", ", roles)
                    </td>
                    <td>@(user.IsActive ? "Yes" : "No")</td>
                    <td>
                        <!-- Ban/Unban -->
                        <form asp-action="ToggleUserActive" asp-controller="Administrator" method="post" class="d-inline">
                            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="@user.Id" />
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm @(user.IsActive ? "btn-danger" : "btn-success")"
                                    data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#confirmModal-@user.Id">
                            @(user.IsActive ? "Ban" : "Unban")
                            </button>
                        </form>

                        <!-- Change Role -->
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#roleModal-@user.Id">
                            Change Role
                        </button>

                        <!-- Modal Ban/Unban -->
                        <div class="modal fade" id="confirmModal-@user.Id" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h5 class="modal-title">Підтвердження дії</h5>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        Ви впевнені, що хочете @(user.IsActive ? "заблокувати" : "розблокувати") користувача <b>@user.FirstName @user.LastName</b>?
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-footer">
                                        <form asp-action="ToggleUserActive" asp-controller="Administrator" method="post">
                                            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="@user.Id" />
                                            <button type="submit" class="btn @(user.IsActive ? "btn-danger" : "btn-success")">
                                                Так, @(user.IsActive ? "Ban" : "Unban")
                                            </button>
                                        </form>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Скасувати</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Modal Change Role -->
                        <div class="modal fade" id="roleModal-@user.Id" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h5 class="modal-title">Change Role for @user.FirstName @user.LastName</h5>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <form asp-action="ChangeUserRole" asp-controller="Administrator" method="post">
                                            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="@user.Id" />
                                            <div class="mb-3">
                                                <label class="form-label">Select new role</label>
                                                <select name="role" class="form-select" required>
                                                    <option value="Student" selected="@(await UserManager.IsInRoleAsync(user, "Student"))">Student</option>
                                                    <option value="Teacher" selected="@(await UserManager.IsInRoleAsync(user, "Teacher"))">Teacher</option>
                                                    <option value="Administrator" selected="@(await UserManager.IsInRoleAsync(user, "Administrator"))">Administrator</option>
                                                </select>
                                            </div>
                                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Save</button>
                                        </form>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </td>
                </tr>
        }
    </tbody>
</table>